sql:
SELECT tissue_name
FROM tissue_types
WHERE tissue_structure = 'solid';

external_knowledge:
Top accessed datasets refer to the datasets with the highest number of access events in the access_logs table; 
Average cell count refers to the mean number of cells of the specified type in the dataset_details table; 
Average rating refers to the mean rating score for the dataset in the dataset_ratings table;
A user group is considered to have shared a dataset the most if it has the highest share count for that dataset in the dataset_shares table.

sql:
SELECT AVG(rating_score) AS average_rating
FROM dataset_ratings
WHERE dataset_id = '0';

SELECT dataset_name
FROM datasets
WHERE dataset_id = '1';

SELECT dataset_id, cell_count
FROM dataset_details
WHERE tissue_ontology_term_id = '1';

SELECT analysis_type, COUNT(*) AS analysis_count
FROM data_analysis
GROUP BY analysis_type;

SELECT COUNT(*) AS public_share_count
FROM dataset_shares
WHERE share_type = 'public';

SELECT AVG(cell_count) AS average_cell_count
FROM dataset_details
WHERE dataset_id = '1';

SELECT rating_score
FROM dataset_ratings
WHERE dataset_id = '1';
